code package illustrating flexible indirect register with uvm. 
more info is available at dvcon2017-us. session 5.1 tuesday feb 28, 3pm

in short:

- code is available under the apache license
- code is UVM12 compatible, to run use something like

cd test && xrun -uvmhome CDNS-1.2 -f run.f